<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Admin Rights Granted</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f7fc;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .email-container {
            background-color: #ffffff;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 30px auto;
            border-radius: 8px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #0066cc;
            padding: 20px;
            color: #ffffff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h2 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 24px;
        }
        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .content p {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #333;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f1f1f1;
            padding: 15px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #0066cc;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        .footer a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #0066cc;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="email-container">
        <!-- Header -->
        <div class="header">
            <h2>Admin Rights Granted</h2>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Content -->
        <div class="content">
            <p>Dear <strong><%= UserName %></strong>,</p>
            <p>We are pleased to inform you that you have been granted Admin Rights for your account. You now have the ability to manage and control your bookings, edit users rights, and other administrative tasks within the system.</p>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please feel free to contact us at <a href="mailto:ayeshaMubasher28@gmail.com">ayeshaMubasher28@gmail.com</a>.</p>
            <p>Thank you for being part of the EasyPark system!</p>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Footer -->
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best Regards,<br> The EasyPark Team</p>
            <p><a href="mailto:ayeshaMubasher28@gmail.com">Contact Support</a></p>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
